    "description": "Step into the shoes of a resourceful refugee in &quot;Inauthentic Hummus,&quot; an engaging time-management game that blends strategy with heartwarming storytelling. You run a bustling food truck, serving up &quot;almost&quot; authentic ethnic foods to a diverse and growing customer base.<br><br>Your mission is clear: upgrade your tools, ingredients, and food truck to serve your customers swiftly and efficiently. Each dish you prepare brings you closer to your ultimate goal—earning your citizenship and securing passports for your family within a 30-day window.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083120/extras/c63bd9a375a70200da445e9fbded49bd.poster.avif?t=1722999911\" width=600 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083120/extras/c63bd9a375a70200da445e9fbded49bd.webm?t=1722999911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083120/extras/c63bd9a375a70200da445e9fbded49bd.mp4?t=1722999911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Face the daily challenges of running a mobile kitchen</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast-Paced gameplay with a focus on pleasing customers</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Invest in better equipment, ingredients, and pay your truck debt</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pass your Civics exam and qualify for an apartment</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Discover the story of your escape from Iraqiland and save your family from the war</li></ul>",
